Linux Installation
------------------

AudioCropper requires Sox with MP3 support. Sox can be installed with the folowing command:

    sudo apt-get install sox libsox-fmt-mp3

If you want to other formats than MP3 the corresponding Sox package has to be
installed. If you want to install all Format Packages for Sox you can use the
following command:

    sudo apt-get install libsox-fmt-all

When the Sox installation is completed download and unzip AudioCropper.
Change into the direcktory in witch you just unziped AudioCropper and install
it with the following command:

    sudo ./setup.py install


